{"tid":1222061,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用戶憤怒！華為手機突然在鎖機畫面強行植入 Booking.com 廣告","createTime":"2019-06-14T10:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T09:04:38.000Z","uid":1130,"like":246,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"95ca1385e1b9a028411f51034ec34359b20c1a5c","tid":1222061,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/14/huawei-smartphone-booking-com-wallpaper-ads/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Fhuawei-smartphone-booking-com-wallpaper-ads%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2560fa82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/06/14/huawei-smartphone-booking-com-wallpaper-ads/</a><br />\n<br />\n華為被美國封鎖，令 Google 不能授權華為的手機使用 Android，令海外手機的銷情告急。不過，來自 AndroidPolice 的報導，大量華為手機用戶突然看到鎖機畫面出現 <a href=\"http://Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=64228f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com</a> 字樣出現在 Wallpaper 上，當中包括 P30 Pro、P20、P20 Lite、Honor 10 及 P20 Pro。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用戶全是使用預設於手機的 Wallpaper，無數用戶感到不滿，上載圖片到 Twitter 。而暫時已確認出現類似廣告的地區，最少有英國、荷蘭、愛爾蘭、南非、挪威和德國。而想移除廣告的方法，就是更變其他自訂 Wallpaper，不用華為提供 Wallpaper 的才行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vDMr6MZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvDMr6MZ.png&h=c1ee1b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FX6WKyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFX6WKyF.png&h=bde8fd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnnu4yG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnnnu4yG.png&h=cb266d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba48e44362c4636e8e3c98c319933ad1e1b1305d","tid":1222061,"uid":187889,"like":196,"dislike":0,"score":196,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 人好人姐用華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bd6146642d9de7f53085b0d3bee92ef182b753","tid":1222061,"uid":38794,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"光明正大，係前面，好過鬼鬼鼠鼠係後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692767c63e2af881d30063306a2d6a2f8ea26a69","tid":1222061,"uid":1130,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Ytzis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FYtzis.jpg&h=68482c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d46f4c0106303e32a30e6a90d82745a317c3c3fb","tid":1222061,"uid":38794,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"692767c63e2af881d30063306a2d6a2f8ea26a69","tid":1222061,"uid":1130,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Ytzis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FYtzis.jpg&h=68482c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=20c80f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">booking.com</a> 其實有無想過用戶感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bda602b4cc7205b5873ac4118703d014e25e62e","tid":1222061,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/